Comment: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:17.52,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中文字幕\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}英文字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:17.52,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是第一次 欧空局在中国组织进行航天员培训活动\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}For the first time ever, ESA has been conducting astronaut training activities in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:25.20,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Matthias Maurer和Samantha Cristoforetti最近和7名中国航天员在一起\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Matthias Maurer and Samantha Cristoforetti recently joined 7 Chinese astronauts -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:31.56,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者说太空人 进行了9天的海上生存培训课程 在中国滨海城市烟台市外\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}or Taikonauts - for a nine day sea survival training session off China's coastal city of Yantai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:39.57,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们基本上是在为异常着陆而进行培训\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}We are basically practising what would happen if there was an off-nominal landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:53.75,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使用急救设备 并且自主地离开返回舱\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}the rescue equipment and exiting of course the re-entry capsule autonomously.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:55.77,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}穿着压力服\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Wearing pressure suits,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:00.38,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宇航员进入了神舟飞船的实体模型 之后被释放到海里\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}the astronauts entered a mock-up Shenzhou capsule that was then released into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.76,0:01:05.93,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Samantha和Matthias分别和另外两个中国航天员组队\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Samantha and Matthias were each teamed with two Taikonauts –
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.42,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种配置更接近于实际情况\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}who between them have considerable spaceflight experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:13.15,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在穿上绝缘且有浮力的服装后\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}After donning insulation and buoyancy suits,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:16.92,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们演练了有船和直升机情况下的急救程序\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}they practised rescue procedures with both a ship and a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:23.58,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太空任务可能是充满意外的 而类似这样的培训课程\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Space missions can be unpredictable – and training exercises such as these
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:27.30,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以确保宇航员应对各种情况\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}ensure that astronauts are prepared for every eventuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:43.03,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有个巨大的使用在公海上的海上生存救援船\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}we have a huge sea-survival rescue ship which is usually employed on the high seas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.80,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以到目前为止 是很好的装备和体验\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}so very good equipment and a very good experience so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:52.92,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和Samantha还有Matthias一起在中国的还有一个欧空局的飞行外科医生\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Accompanying Samantha and Matthias in China were an ESA flight surgeon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:58.42,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及一个培训专家 了解了文化的细微差异\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}and a training specialist – who gained insights into the different cultural nuances and approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.52,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这种医药有着上千年的历史\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}which has thousands of years of history,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.85,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是他们会把中医与世界上最先进的医药知识结合在一起\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}with the most advanced medical knowledge that we can find now in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.00,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这里的培训组织得很好\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Training here is very, very well organised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.37,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但实际上这之间的差异并不大\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}but actually they are not that far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:30.80,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就意味着我们在培训组织中能够找到共同语言\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}so it means that we find common words and common understanding in the way they also organise training,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:35.16,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以 对我们来说 这是一个非常好的信号 可以和中国人进一步合作\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}so for us it's a very good sign for further co-operation with the Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:40.39,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这次培训不是两家机构的第一次合作了\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}This training exercise wasn't the first collaboration between the two space agencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:47.76,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}2016年7月 中国航天员叶光富参加了欧空局在撒丁岛的洞穴课程\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}In July 2016, Chinese astronaut Ye Guangfu joined ESA's caving course in Sardinia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:52.07,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在多元文化团队的氛围中 体验极端环境\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}to experience an extreme environment as part of a multicultural crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:59.26,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这两项活动都源自于2015年的协议\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Both activities stem from the 2015 agreement to boost collaboration
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:02.15,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来加速欧空局和中国载人航天办公室的合作\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}between ESA and the China Manned Space Agency -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:08.96,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最终目标是在2022年让欧洲航天员进入中国空间站\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}with the ultimate goal of flying European astronauts onboard the Chinese space station from 2022.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:26.26,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能和中国航天员去未来的中国空间站\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}flying with the Taikonauts to the future Chinese space station,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:30.15,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以当然了 如果我有这样的机会 我会很激动\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}so of course I would be thrilled if I had that opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.51,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}由中国航天员中心组织\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Organised by the Astronaut Centre of China
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:38.15,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以及交通运输部北海救助局合作\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}in co-operation with the Ministry of Transport's Beihai Rescue Bureau,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:43.16,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}本次培训班是实现长期合作的一个重要步骤\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}this training session has been an important step towards long-term collaboration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:48.08,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其他培训机会 联合活动正在酝酿中\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}Other training opportunities and joint activities are in the pipeline –
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:54.04,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}目的是帮助欧空局和中国载人航天办公室促进互相的了解\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50}{\blur4}with the aim of helping ESA and the China Manned Space Agency to get to know one another better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:43.08,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们不会在陆地上着陆 而是在海里溅落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.86,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们将不得不独立生存一段时间 并使用急救艇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:30.04,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到目前为止 培训给我的体验很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:36.23,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中国人准备真的很周全 装备很高级 我们进行了直升机空运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:03.16,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这个培训中 我有机会与中国的医疗同事们密切合作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:08.65,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}关于他们如何现代化传统中国医药 我对此非常印象深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:22.78,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们有着不同的培训方法 继承自国际空间站的项目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:14.38,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们在这儿做的这个合作培训是合作的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:21.36,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们都希望有朝一日 在2020年代初 让一个欧洲航天员
